# Portfolio Manager — Azure Architecture Diagram

## Architecture Overview

The Portfolio Manager platform consists of two Azure Container Apps running in a shared Container Apps Environment:

1. **MCP Server** — Hosts 3 MCP endpoints (Finnhub, Portfolio, CRM) that serve as the tool layer for both the Declarative Agent and Digital Worker. Connects to Azure OpenAI for AI-powered widget rendering, Dataverse/D365 CRM for enterprise data, and Finnhub for live market data.

2. **Digital Worker** — An autonomous A365 agent with its own Teams presence and mailbox. Calls the MCP Server for portfolio/CRM/market data, Azure OpenAI for LLM inference, Azure AI Services for Voice Live, and Azure Bot Service for Teams messaging. Runs 5 scheduled jobs for autonomous operations.

## Data Flow

- **Interactive (M365 Copilot):** User → M365 Copilot → Declarative Agent → MCP Server → Dataverse / D365 CRM / Finnhub
- **Interactive (Teams DM):** User → Teams → Bot Service → Digital Worker → OpenAI + MCP Server
- **Voice:** Browser → WebSocket → Digital Worker → Azure AI Services (Voice Live) → OpenAI
- **Scheduled:** Container App Jobs → Digital Worker `/api/scheduled/*` → MCP Server → Email (Graph) + Teams Channel (Webhook)

```mermaid
graph TD
    %% User Interfaces
    subgraph "User Interfaces"
        copilot["M365 Copilot<br/>(Declarative Agent + 12 Widgets)"]
        teams["Microsoft Teams<br/>(Digital Worker Chat + Channel Alerts)"]
        voice["Voice Interface<br/>(Browser WebSocket)"]
    end

    %% Services
    subgraph "Compute Resources"
        subgraph containerappenv["Azure Container Apps Environment (East US)"]
            azurecontainerapps_mcpserver("`**MCP Server**
            3 MCP Endpoints
            40 Tools | 12 Widgets
            Port 3000`")
            azurecontainerapps_digitalworker("`**Digital Worker**
            A365 Agent + @openai/agents
            26 Function Tools
            Port 3978`")
        end
        containerappenv:::cluster

        subgraph jobs["Azure Container App Jobs"]
            job_briefing["pm-job-briefing<br/>Weekdays 9am"]
            job_monitor["pm-job-monitor<br/>Every 5 min"]
            job_fx["pm-job-fx<br/>Every 15 min"]
            job_compliance["pm-job-compliance<br/>Monday 8am"]
            job_earnings["pm-job-earnings<br/>Weekdays 7am"]
        end
    end

    subgraph "AI Services"
        azureopenai["`**Azure OpenAI Service**
        GPT-4o`"]
        azureaiservices["`**Azure AI Services**
        Voice Live + HD Neural Voice`"]
    end

    subgraph "Data & Identity"
        azurecontainerregistry["`**Azure Container Registry**
        <YOUR_ACR_NAME>.azurecr.io`"]
        dataverse["`**Microsoft Dataverse**
        pm_portfolioholdings
        pm_dealtracker`"]
        d365crm["`**Dynamics 365 CRM**
        Accounts, Contacts
        Opportunities, Activities`"]
        msgraph["`**Microsoft Graph**
        Mail.Send, User.Read.All
        Chat.ReadWrite`"]
        entraid["`**Microsoft Entra ID**
        Agent Blueprint + Graph App
        Agentic OAuth`"]
    end

    subgraph "External"
        finnhub["`**Finnhub API**
        Quotes, News, SEC
        Earnings, FX, IPOs`"]
        webhook["`**Power Automate**
        Workflows Webhook
        Portfolio Alerts Channel`"]
    end

    %% User connections
    copilot --> azurecontainerapps_mcpserver
    teams --> |"Bot Service"| azurecontainerapps_digitalworker
    voice --> |"WebSocket"| azurecontainerapps_digitalworker

    %% MCP Server connections
    azurecontainerapps_mcpserver --> |"/finnhub/mcp"| finnhub
    azurecontainerapps_mcpserver --> |"/portfolio/mcp"| dataverse
    azurecontainerapps_mcpserver --> |"/crm/mcp"| d365crm
    azurecontainerapps_mcpserver -.-> |"system-identity"| azurecontainerregistry

    %% Digital Worker connections
    azurecontainerapps_digitalworker --> |"MCP Client"| azurecontainerapps_mcpserver
    azurecontainerapps_digitalworker --> |"LLM Inference"| azureopenai
    azurecontainerapps_digitalworker --> |"Voice Live"| azureaiservices
    azurecontainerapps_digitalworker --> |"Email + Users"| msgraph
    azurecontainerapps_digitalworker --> |"Channel Alerts"| webhook
    azurecontainerapps_digitalworker -.-> |"Agentic Auth"| entraid
    azurecontainerapps_digitalworker -.-> |"system-identity"| azurecontainerregistry

    %% Scheduled Jobs
    job_briefing --> |"POST /api/scheduled/briefing"| azurecontainerapps_digitalworker
    job_monitor --> |"POST /api/scheduled/monitor"| azurecontainerapps_digitalworker
    job_fx --> |"POST /api/scheduled/fx"| azurecontainerapps_digitalworker
    job_compliance --> |"POST /api/scheduled/compliance"| azurecontainerapps_digitalworker
    job_earnings --> |"POST /api/scheduled/earnings"| azurecontainerapps_digitalworker

    %% Styling
    classDef cluster fill:#e8f4f8,stroke:#0078d4,stroke-width:2px
    classDef ai fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#ff8f00,stroke-width:2px
    classDef data fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#2e7d32,stroke-width:2px
    classDef external fill:#fce4ec,stroke:#c62828,stroke-width:2px
    classDef user fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1565c0,stroke-width:2px

    class azureopenai,azureaiservices ai
    class dataverse,d365crm,msgraph,entraid,azurecontainerregistry data
    class finnhub,webhook external
    class copilot,teams,voice user
```
